<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Body>
    <Title>南极基地暴发疫情！</Title>
    <ReportTime type="absTime">2020-12-22T00:00</ReportTime>环球日报
    <Content>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>据
                <Event eid="e1">
                    <Participant sid="s1" type="agent">智利《第三版时报》</Participant>
                    <Time tid="t1" type="relTime">12月22日</Time>
                    <Denoter did="d1" type="statement">报道</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e2">
                    <Location lid="l2">智利</Location>的
                    <Participant sid="s2">南极</Participant>
                    <Object sid="s2" type="agent">基地</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">暴发</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o2" type="recipient">疫情</Object>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e3">
                    <Participant sid="s3" type="agent">36人</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d3" type="operation">感染</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o3" type="recipient">新冠病毒</Object>
                </Event>
            </Sentence>。
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e4">
                    <Location lid="l4">智利</Location>
                    <Participant sid="s4" type="agent">陆军机构</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d4" type="statement">说</Denoter>
                </Event>，现在
                <Event eid="e5">
                    <Object sid="s5" type="agent">基地</Object>已经彻底
                    <Denoter did="d5" type="operation">消毒</Denoter>
                </Event>
            </Sentence>。
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e6">
                    <Object sid="s6" type="agent">报道</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d6" type="statement">称</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e7">
                    <Location lid="l7">智利</Location>在
                    <Location lid="l7">南极</Location>的
                    <Location lid="l7">贝尔纳多·奥希金斯·里克尔梅基地</Location>共有
                    <Participant sid="s7" type="agent">36人</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d7" type="operation">感染</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o7" type="recipient">新冠病毒</Object>
                </Event>，这次疫情是
                <Event eid="e8">
                    <Object sid="s8" type="agent">海军萨亨托·阿尔德亚舰</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d8" type="operation">访问</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o8" type="recipient">基地</Object>
                </Event>导致的结果，
                <Event eid="e9">
                    <Object sid="s9" type="agent">该舰</Object>后来
                    <Denoter did="d9" type="emergency">被爆</Denoter>舰上船员中有新冠肺炎病例
                </Event>
            </Sentence>。
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e10">
                    <Location lid="l10">智利</Location>
                    <Participant sid="s10" type="agent">陆军</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d10" type="statement">发表</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o10" type="recipient">声明</Object>解释说
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e11">
                    <Participant sid="s11" type="agent">感染人员</Participant>在
                    <Denoter did="d11" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o11" type="recipient">症状</Object>
                </Event>之后已
                <Event eid="e12">
                    <Denoter did="d12" type="operation">撤离</Denoter>
                </Event>，然后
                <Event eid="e13">
                    <Denoter did="d13" type="operation">接受</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o13" type="recipient">核酸检测</Object>
                </Event>
            </Sentence>。
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e14">
                    <Object sid="s14" type="agent">声明</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d14" type="statement">解释</Denoter>说
                </Event>：“
                <Event eid="e15">
                    <Participant sid="s15" type="agent">36人</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d15" type="operation">检测</Denoter>结果呈阳性
                </Event>，其中26人是陆军人员，还有10人是承包商公司的平民，
                <Event eid="e16">
                    <Object sid="s16" type="agent">该公司</Object>正在
                    <Location lid="l16">南极基地</Location>
                    <Time tid="t16" type="absTime">定期</Time>
                    <Denoter did="d16" type="operation">进行</Denoter>
                    <Object sid="s16" type="agent">维护工作</Object>
                </Event>
            </Sentence>。”
        </Paragraph>
    </Content>
